OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Ftonight with scattered showers moving
OL,7,Fin from the west, some turning heavy
OL,8,Fat times. Fairly mild under the
OL,9,Fblanket of cloud with temperatures in
OL,10,Fdouble figures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FLow cloud to start with, but
OL,13,Flifting through the morning and into
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Isolated showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping, with sunny spells in
OL,16,Fbetween. Warm, but cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
