OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FScattered showers continuing into
OL,7,FMonday with heavy rain and possible
OL,8,Fthunderstorms with a mix of hail.
OL,9,FStaying unsettled through the week as
OL,10,Ftemperatures return to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
